00:03:37.563 --> 00:03:39.830
to whom I owe the duty of doing the

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:42.105
research and examination of

00:03:42.106 --> 00:03:43.679
the entire cryptocurrency space

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:45.837
and making recommendations on what I think

00:03:45.848 --> 00:03:48.178
are the most compelling projects out there.

00:03:48.412 --> 00:03:50.390
Within cryptocurrency, I also specialize

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.390
in tokens that do what I think is the

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:54.597
"killer app" of Nakamoto consensus,

00:03:54.608 --> 00:03:56.017
